# Bobby Singer - Dialogue File
# Each section is a callable dialogue function
# Format: @function_name followed by lines of speaker:text
# Conditions and branching can be added with #if, #goto

@greeting
Bobby: You idjits better be prepared before heading out.
Bobby: I've got some supplies if you need 'em.
Bobby: Also, watch your back. Something ain't right in this town.

@supplies
Bobby: Let me see what I got in the truck.
Bobby: Here, take this shotgun. Rock salt rounds.
Bobby: And some holy water. Never leave home without it.

@warning
Bobby: Listen to me, boy.
Bobby: There's something big coming. I can feel it.
Bobby: You and Sam need to stick together on this one.
Dean: We always do, Bobby.

@after_battle
Bobby: You boys alright?
Dean: Nothing a cold beer won't fix.
Bobby: I'll hold you to that. Now get moving.

@farewell
Bobby: Stay safe out there, ya hear?
Bobby: And call me if things go sideways.
Dean: Will do, Bobby.
